    "desc": "Handcrafted goat milk soaps made with raw goat milk for our own small herd of goats. Our does are hand milked and the milk is combined with the finest oils for cold process soapmaking. We create a complete line of body care products including goat milk & honey lotion, body butter, scrubs and balms. ",
    "navbar": "Home\nGoat Milk Soap\nSkin Care\nGifts\nRed Barn\nMeet The Makers 2022\nCalendar\nContact\nWholesale",
    "text": "Garden Goat Soap\n0\nOur family has been handcrafting goat milk soap using the cold process method since 2010. We use only raw milk from our herd of dairy goats and the finest oils available. All of our soaps are made in small batches, hand cut, and allowed to cure before being wrapped and labeled for you.\nIn 2021 we moved to Twin Goat Farm located in beautiful\nPittstown, NJ and started\nGifts from the Red Barn.\nOur seasonal craft pop up shops featuring some of our favorite artists, crafters, farm goods and of course our handcrafted soaps, lotions and gift sets. \nCheck out the Red Barn Tab\nfor upcoming shows.\nComing soon\nfresh baked goodies from\nBuffie Bakes!\n We are excited to offer\nshopping at our Red Barn\nFridays & Saturdays 11 till 4\nSundays 12 till 3\n619 Sidney Rd. W. \nPittstown, NJ 08867\nBrowse & Shop Online\nGoat Milk Soap\nSkin Care\nGift Ideas\nOur Featured Products\nFig\nOut of stock\nPumpkin Spice\nPrice\n$7.00\nOrchid\nPrice\n$7.00\nOud\nPrice\n$7.00\nHome\nGoat Milk Soap\nSkin Care\nGifts\nRed Barn\nMeet The Makers 2022\nCalendar\nContact\nWholesale\n© gardengoatsoap\nProudly created with Wix.com",
